# Example Dataset for Reproducibility
#
# Structure of `data_example`:
# ----------------------------------------
# `data_example` is a list of length 4,
# corresponding to four spatial slices.
#
# Each slice is itself a list containing four elements:
#
# 1) Gene expression matrix (1024 × 100)
#    - 1024 spatial spots
#    - 100 genes
#
# 2) Spatial coordinate matrix (1024 × 2)
#    - x and y coordinates of each spot
#
# 3) Covariate matrix (1024 × 6)
#    - Six-dimensional covariate information per spot
#
# 4) Tissue boundary data frame
#    - Boundary information required as input for the spVC method
#
# 5) Tissue cluster label (1024×1)
#    - layer label information required as input for the DESpace method
#
